data.description:
LIVE IN THE COUNTRY! Enjoy this Ravenna Township home on over 6 acres. Hunting rights on property! Features plenty of space to entertain with ample storage. Home has a huge four-season porch that can also function as a spacious living or dining room depending on your family's needs.  A short drive to the scenic Mississippi River for boating and recreation, in addition to numerous hiking and biking trails in the woods and along the river. Convenient to Hastings and Red Wing for shopping, dining and exploring the environment. Just a few miles from Treasure Island Resort and Casino for top-notch entertainment from national talent, family bowling alley and gambling for the grown-ups. Be sure to visit Miesville for famous burgers, amateur league baseball and supper club! 

New roof installed in 2020. Owner built on addition in 2008, and added all-new electrical and septic system in 2008. Estate sale. Buyer's agent to verify all measurements. Quick close available!
